        <num>CC 3498</num>
        <heading>3498.  Actions on negotiable and nonnegotiable instruments</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3498.  Actions on negotiable and nonnegotiable instruments
Actions on instruments, whether negotiable or not, and on promissory notes, whether negotiable or not, are subject to a liberative prescription of five years.  This prescription commences to run from the day payment is exigible.</p>
        </content>
